column19: SAFE and COMPETITIVE for all divisions!Each player will receive an NFL reversible game jersey and flag belt when signing up. Team practices may start any time after August 21st with the the regular season kicking off the first Saturday in September after Labor Day and runs through the first few weeks of November. We have an 7-8 game regular season with playoffs. Top four teams from each division qualify for playoffs.Games run around 60-70 mins. MYFF has a small concession stand set up at the fields.
